<HEAD>British Petroleum Gives Up Plans For Drill Near Pooh Corner</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   British Petroleum has dropped its bid to drill for
oil next to a southern English forest where A.A. Milne conjured up
