<2ND_LINE>AM-Chambers, 1st Ld - Writethru, a0865,0123</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Tape Shows a Partying Chambers in the Days Before His Trial</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 2nd graf to restore 1st reference to Chambers</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By RONALD POWERS</BYLINE>
